/02/20231101_Salsa_EBike_6_DSC0725-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20231101_Salsa_EBike_6_DSC0725-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20231101_Salsa_EBike_6_DSC0725-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20231101_Salsa_EBike_6_DSC0725-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20231101_Salsa_EBike_7_DSC4399-scaled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20231101_Salsa_EBike_7_DSC4399-800x533.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20231101_Salsa_EBike_7_DSC4399-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20231101_Salsa_EBike_7_DSC4399-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20231101_Salsa_EBike_7_DSC4399-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20231101_Salsa_EBike_7_DSC4399-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20231101_Salsa_EBike_7_DSC4399-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20231101_Salsa_EBike_7_DSC4399-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20231101_Salsa_EBike_7_DSC4399-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Moving to the MTB side of things, it appears Salsa will have two full supsension platforms. The Moraine will be their light electric trail bike with Split Pivot suspension. The Notch is their full. power enduro ebike with Split Pivot supsension. Other than what we covered with the<a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/salsa-cycles-prototype-emtb-gravel-ebikes/\" target=\"_blank\"> prototype at Sea Otter</a>, details on these two are TBA when they launch this Spring. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.salsacycles.com/bikes/ebike\" target=\"_blank\">salsacycles.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/salsa-cycles-electric-bikes-confluence-light-e-gravel-ebike/\">Salsa Cycles Gets Electric with Confluence Light e-Gravel Bike, More eBikes Coming</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"e4dc2a05fc9a89c9d77b0c12e0cfd7da443909a40b4cedc76483eb0ab8033469","category":"Cycling"}